</p>
<p>79. Women and girls displaced by natural disasters have also been subject to rape, sexual 
abuse, early and forced marriage, and trafficking,<b>87</b> with long-term impact on women&#8217;s rights 
and welfare in the post-crisis or post-conflict situation.<b>88</b> The stigmatization, and sometimes even 
